        public static ImmutableSortedSet<BuildRule> androidResOnly(ImmutableSortedSet<BuildRule> deps)
        Filters out the set of android_resource() dependencies from deps. As a special case, if an android_prebuilt_aar() appears in the deps, the android_resource() that corresponds to the AAR will also be included in the output.
